// the browser once the correct password is entered, so the source ships
// ciphertext, not the proposal.
//
// Change the password below (PASSWORD) and rebuild to rotate it.
// noindex + excluded from the sitemap (see astro.config sitemap filter).
// Brand fonts (ITC Souvenir / Avant Garde) are licensed; we approximate with the
// site's serif/sans and can embed the real fonts if licensed.
// ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
